{"type": "article", "id": 17486, "title": "蛋糕架", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-13T06:10:13Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 17, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606144619k6sZhVawcoGU9KWI.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一个蛋糕架，也可以装一些水果和点心。它有三种不同的体型，对应深绿色、棕色和蓝色的底座和黄铜的盖子，有古典的优雅。黄铜的盖子有亮丽的光泽，也让蛋糕架的整体外形有些像甜筒冰激凌，带着点可爱的气质。设计者是米兰的 80 后设计师 Ilaria Innocenti，她将蛋糕架命名为“belle“，意为美女，也是突出它的秀丽和优雅。<a href=\"http://www.ilariai.com/product/#/belle/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144614kYsa2BvTHpNULC9f.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144615RrkIG2giUjCpAy8v.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"711\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.86919315\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144616luVyZFkQmY3g9OdS.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261446165kQVSJMo4UmZt6Xf.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"719\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.87897311\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}